HEADWORD: Blackfeet
<hw>Black"feet`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos>
<fld>(Ethn.)</fld> <def>A tribe of North American Indians formerly
inhabiting the country from the upper Missouri River to the
Saskatchewan, but now much reduced in numbers.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

